## <a href="/search?keynode=FreeCAD%20Mesh%20workbench" target="_blank">Mesh workbench</a>

- Solid to mesh
  - 2 key parameters
    - Surface deviation
      - control precision
    - Angular deviation
      - control deviation allowed in the model's angles
      - particularly for curves and sharp edges.
- Key functionalities
